  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Content-Security-Policy: script-src 'self' 'sha256-nRcgRt3XNN0aZXdzMDUhXYSzvNDbxXeNTBXS8ajcR38=' https://*.simplesocket.net https://*.exotek.co https://*.googleapis.com https://*.cloudflare.com; frame-src * blob:

